875
00:36:17,930 --> 00:36:19,290
just come clean now.

876
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:21,050
I swear, there's nothing else.

877
00:36:22,550 --> 00:36:23,870
I just didn't want to make you angry,

878
00:36:23,870 --> 00:36:25,870
-so I…
-You don’t want me to be angry?

879
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:27,830
If you hadn't done anything wrong,

880
00:36:27,830 --> 00:36:30,050
why would you even worry about my feelings?

881
00:36:30,050 --> 00:36:31,780
Didn't want to make me upset...

882
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,520
Yang, let's do this.

883
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:35,940
Your mom has never liked me anyway.

884
00:36:36,510 --> 00:36:37,640
She's always saying

885
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:38,920
how great Feng Jing is.

886
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,920
Why don't you two just get remarried

887
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:43,030
and leave me out of it?

888
00:36:43,030 --> 00:36:43,790
I'm begging you.

889
00:36:43,790 --> 00:36:45,390
I'm begging you.

890
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:47,830
Can you stop making this bigger than it is?

891
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:55,210
Why aren't you asleep?

892
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,350
I'm just going to the bathroom.

893
00:36:57,350 --> 00:36:58,550
I heard

894
00:36:58,550 --> 00:37:00,110
something fall in there.

895
00:37:01,270 --> 00:37:02,410
Oh,

896
00:37:02,510 --> 00:37:03,310
the basin accidentally fell over.

897
00:37:03,310 --> 00:37:05,040
Yeah, it was me. I stepped on it.

898
00:37:05,730 --> 00:37:07,390
Hurry up and use the bathroom,

899
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,090
then get back to bed.

900
00:37:10,180 --> 00:37:11,440
-It’s too late.
-Okay.

901
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,390
I think my mom and Yang

902
00:37:24,390 --> 00:37:26,050
had another fight yesterday.

903
00:37:26,090 --> 00:37:27,010
Again?

904
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:29,230
Did you say

905
00:37:29,230 --> 00:37:30,710
they were getting along lately?

906
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:31,380
No.

907
00:37:31,740 --> 00:37:33,390
You went through all that trouble

908
00:37:33,390 --> 00:37:35,060
jumping in the river for nothing?

909
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,430
Did they break anything this time?

910
00:37:36,430 --> 00:37:37,690
Was there any hitting?

911
00:37:37,830 --> 00:37:38,510
Nope.

912
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,090
I was just guessing.

913
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,830
What do you mean?

914
00:37:41,830 --> 00:37:43,230
You didn't see anything?

915
00:37:43,270 --> 00:37:44,430
When I got home yesterday,

916
00:37:44,430 --> 00:37:46,550
they were acting all weird, just sitting in the living room.

917
00:37:46,550 --> 00:37:48,080
They said they were waiting

918
00:37:48,080 --> 00:37:49,160
to welcome me home.

919
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,280
And then at night,

920
00:37:51,310 --> 00:37:52,670
I heard a noise,

921
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:53,950
like something fell over.

922
00:37:53,950 --> 00:37:55,150
I rushed out to check.

923
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,090
What did you see?

924
00:37:56,310 --> 00:37:57,610
They were both washing their feet.

925
00:37:57,610 --> 00:37:59,000
It looked great.

926
00:37:59,350 --> 00:38:00,350
They said they accidentally

927
00:38:00,350 --> 00:38:01,950
knocked over the washbasin.

928
00:38:03,140 --> 00:38:05,140
Well, that sounds good, doesn't it?

929
00:38:05,750 --> 00:38:07,470
There's another possibility—

930
00:38:07,470 --> 00:38:08,030
they're just not arguing

931
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:09,290
in front of you anymore.

932
00:38:09,290 --> 00:38:10,410
I think so too.

933
00:38:10,630 --> 00:38:11,750
They're probably

934
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:13,750
still worried about you

935
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:15,080
jumping into the river.

936
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:16,540
So in a way, it worked.

937
00:38:16,980 --> 00:38:19,160
Is that a good thing or a bad thing?

938
00:38:19,430 --> 00:38:20,910
Definitely a good thing.

939
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:21,710
Think about it—

940
00:38:21,710 --> 00:38:22,920
they're not arguing like they used to,

941
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,030
which means they're still

942
00:38:24,030 --> 00:38:24,870
considering your feelings.

943
00:38:24,870 --> 00:38:26,350
And if they're not fighting in front of you,

944
00:38:26,350 --> 00:38:27,910
that's less fighting overall,

945
00:38:27,910 --> 00:38:29,110
right?

946
00:38:31,230 --> 00:38:32,270
Last time,

947
00:38:32,270 --> 00:38:33,910
I yelled at Yang Songbai.

948
00:38:34,350 --> 00:38:35,260
I thought for sure

949
00:38:35,260 --> 00:38:37,030
our relationship was over.

950
00:38:37,360 --> 00:38:38,480
But now that he's back,

951
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,420
he's acting like nothing happened

952
00:38:39,420 --> 00:38:40,950
and is even being nice to me.

953
00:38:41,980 --> 00:38:43,150
That means

954
00:38:43,260 --> 00:38:44,990
your scolding really hit home.

955
00:38:45,190 --> 00:38:46,710
I think you should just pretend

956
00:38:46,710 --> 00:38:47,790
like you don't know anything,

957
00:38:47,790 --> 00:38:49,030
and when they don't fight in front of you,

958
00:38:49,030 --> 00:38:49,990
act really happy

959
00:38:49,990 --> 00:38:51,230
about it.

960
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:52,870
It's like positive reinforcement, you know?

961
00:38:52,870 --> 00:38:53,870
My dad always says

962
00:38:53,870 --> 00:38:56,870
that even adults need encouragement from their kids.

963
00:39:08,390 --> 00:39:09,190
Who's this?

964
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:12,440
It's Qiang Xiaowa.

965
00:39:13,270 --> 00:39:14,200
What's going on?

966
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:15,820
What's going on?

967
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:28,160
-Class begins.
-Stand up.

968
00:39:28,630 --> 00:39:31,840
Good morning, teacher.

969
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:32,430
Sit down.

970
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:46,340
Miaomiao,

971
00:39:47,220 --> 00:39:49,370
between you and Qiang Xiaowa?

972
00:39:50,460 --> 00:39:52,010
What could there possibly be between us?

973
00:39:52,010 --> 00:39:53,610
Don't think I didn't notice.

974
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,910
You two were talking yesterday.

975
00:39:55,910 --> 00:39:56,790
Today he's acting like this.

976
00:39:56,790 --> 00:39:57,790
Not only are you not happy,

977
00:39:57,790 --> 00:39:58,970
you're not even talking.

978
00:39:58,970 --> 00:40:00,290
Something's definitely up.

979
00:40:00,290 --> 00:40:01,420
Nothing's going on.

980
00:40:01,950 --> 00:40:03,590
I just realized that

981
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:05,190
not everyone can be friends.

982
00:40:13,350 --> 00:40:14,490
What's going on?

983
00:40:14,770 --> 00:40:16,030
You put on the uniform,

984
00:40:16,250 --> 00:40:17,170
cut your hair,

985
00:40:17,780 --> 00:40:19,040
and cleaned up nicely.

986
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,970
It's none of your business.

987
00:40:24,680 --> 00:40:26,740
Did Miaomiao ask you to cut your hair?

988
00:40:27,160 --> 00:40:28,820
You really listen to her, huh?

989
00:40:29,940 --> 00:40:31,830
Why should I listen to her?

990
00:40:34,910 --> 00:40:35,430
You...

991
00:40:36,050 --> 00:40:37,380
Where are you going now?

992
00:40:38,590 --> 00:40:39,590
Breaking news.

993
00:40:40,190 --> 00:40:41,030
I just saw

994
00:40:41,030 --> 00:40:42,510
the police at our school!

995
00:40:43,240 --> 00:40:44,080
The police?

996
00:40:44,100 --> 00:40:44,790
Of course.

997
00:40:44,820 --> 00:40:46,920
Who else would it be, security guards?

998
00:40:46,920 --> 00:40:48,720
Why are the police at our school?

999
00:40:48,910 --> 00:40:50,150
No idea.

1000
00:40:50,150 --> 00:40:52,210
Maybe something happened at school.

1001
00:40:52,590 --> 00:40:54,430
There are bad people at school.

1002
00:40:54,730 --> 00:40:56,580
The police should've come a long time ago.

1003
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,090
Tao.

1004
00:40:57,990 --> 00:40:59,020
Where did the police go?

1005
00:40:59,020 --> 00:41:00,150
I think

1006
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:01,540
they went toward the office.

1007
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:03,590
I wasn't about to stare at them too long.

1008
00:41:03,590 --> 00:41:04,750
Why not?

1009
00:41:05,030 --> 00:41:06,230
It's not like you did anything wrong.

1010
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:08,290
-Well, I...
-Sit down, Zhong Ruitao.

1011
00:41:11,350 --> 00:41:12,310
Yuan Shanqing.

1012
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:14,130
Come with me to the office.

1013
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:17,200
Are the police here for her?

1014
00:41:26,230 --> 00:41:27,030
Sir.

1015
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:30,770
Teacher, are the police here to arrest the bad guy?

1016
00:41:30,770 --> 00:41:31,840
Who told you that?

1017
00:41:32,070 --> 00:41:33,670
Nobody's getting arrested.

1018
00:41:34,290 --> 00:41:35,700
Now focus on class.

1019
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,360
I'm looking for Yuan Shanqing

1020
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,490
for something else.

1021
00:41:38,870 --> 00:41:39,470
Let's go.

1022
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:06,290
Miaomiao.

1023
00:42:06,990 --> 00:42:08,430
Big news.

1024
00:42:08,670 --> 00:42:11,430
Yuan Yong's daughter was taken away by the police.

1025
00:42:11,430 --> 00:42:12,270
Taken away?

1026
00:42:28,580 --> 00:42:30,050
My dad always told me,

1027
00:42:30,510 --> 00:42:31,110
never lose the courage

1028
00:42:31,110 --> 00:42:32,630
to be a good person.

1029
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:35,110
But my well-meaning kindness

1030
00:42:35,270 --> 00:42:36,950
hit a wall with Qiang Xiaowa.

1031
00:42:37,430 --> 00:42:38,390
At that time,

1032
00:42:38,590 --> 00:42:40,070
I always felt like

1033
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:42,230
there was a huge wall between me and them.

1034
00:42:42,230 --> 00:42:44,030
Qiang Xiaowa and Yuan Shanqing—

1035
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:44,630
they always kept people

1036
00:42:44,630 --> 00:42:46,030
at a distance,

1037
00:42:46,460 --> 00:42:48,860
as if they were hiding secrets.

1038
00:42:49,750 --> 00:42:50,230
In every school,

1039
00:42:50,230 --> 00:42:52,040
there are always students like them.

1040
00:42:52,040 --> 00:42:53,350
People label them

1041
00:42:53,350 --> 00:42:54,750
with the same tag:

1042
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:56,140
they must

1043
00:42:56,540 --> 00:42:57,730
be up to no good.

1044
00:42:58,460 --> 00:43:00,030
But no one ever cares about

1045
00:43:00,420 --> 00:43:01,620
who they really are

1046
00:43:02,350 --> 00:43:03,950
or the burdens they carry.
